[http://www.flickr.com/photos/nlireland]  Thank you for attending to my <b>COMPLAINT</b> so quickly. But, you have misunderstood my motives in making same. I was not <b>complaining</b> on my own behalf but rather on behalf of the many keen eyed canine seekers who I believe must feel &quot;left in the lurch&quot; by the non appearance of the species over the past weeks. Rest assured there will be no discombobulation from this quarter tomorrow.


&quot;Every dog must have his day.&quot;
- Jonathan Swift
